summary: This is a brief email exchange between individuals at the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS) regarding scheduling. It mentions an upcoming 'Epstein Brass meeting' on Tuesday and the expectation of receiving a memo by the end of the following week.

keyFacts: The email is internal correspondence from the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
It references a high-level 'Epstein Brass meeting' scheduled for Tuesday, December 10, 2019.
The office expected to deliver a memo related to the Epstein case by the end of the week of December 9, 2019.
